name: Olympic medal count
summary: As the Paris Olympics commence, the race for medals intensifies. NBC New York reveals the current leaderboard, while The Washington Post provides a comprehensive medal tracker for each country. USA TODAY focuses on the United States' medal count, and The New York Times offers an analysis beyond the medal tally. CBS Sports provides a detailed tracker for USA and other participating nations. TIME has compiled a list of countries with the highest medal counts to date. CBS News examines the all-time Olympic medal winners, highlighting the top countries and athletes. The Associated Press presents a complete list of medal winners in Paris, and NBC News delivers live updates, with the United States securing its first gold in the swimming relay on day one. CNN maintains a gold medal tracker to monitor the ongoing competition.

Antetokounmpo played for Greece in the 2024 Paris Olympics, where they were defeated by Canada.
